    "After experimental testing, we discovered that the online version is appropriate for closed-loop systems boxed to the loaded data without requiring additional computation or information.",
    "It only responds to straightforward queries about the loaded data.",
    "This version is more secure for data as the load is not exposed to the web.",
    "The online system responds to broader queries with additional contextualized tips, information, and guidelines to grow operators' knowledge but makes the loaded data available to the company OpenAI.We organize the sections of the manuscript as follows: Section 2 presents a brief literature review and background on some important topics useful in this study, such as the industrial revolutions from the first to the current one (from 1IR to 5IR), the evolution of generative pre-trained transformers (GPT) models with some its popular applications such as ChatGPT and highlight some prevalent chatbot applications in various sectors.",
    "Section 3 sets forth the high-level and detailed architectural design of our industrial bots as well as the theoretical design and expressions to incorporate essential parameters like pollution level and maximum overtime working hours into production decision-making that transform an I4.0 factory to an I5.0 compatible one."
